  "excerpt": "The Alberta Mixed Doubles &amp; Edmonton Doubles Squash Open was last weekend (October 19-21) with a number of teams from the ESC participating. Congratulations to Julie Multamaki and Brooke Rothwell for winning the mixed division, and thank you to Pete Goodings for organizing such a fun tournament. The November doubles ladder is just around the &#8230; Read more",
  "content": "<div class=\"name\">The Alberta Mixed Doubles &amp; Edmonton Doubles Squash Open was last weekend (October 19-21) with a number of teams from the ESC participating. Congratulations to Julie Multamaki and Brooke Rothwell for winning the mixed division, and thank you to Pete Goodings for organizing such a fun tournament.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>The November doubles ladder is just around the corner. You can sign up by following the instructions <a href=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/doubles-news-from-julie/\">here</a>.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>Thank you Sandra for the pictures!</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4089.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5393\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4089.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4089.jpg 600w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4089-225x300.jpg 225w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4089-15x20.jpg 15w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-5394\" src=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101-1.jpg 600w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101-1-300x225.jpg 300w, https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4101-1-20x15.jpg 20w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://edmontonsquashclub.ca/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/IMG_4105.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-5395\" src=\"https:/